- extends is for extending a class.
- implements is for implementing an interface

__construct() - https://www.w3schools.com/php/func_simplexml__construct.asp

- static - https://www.w3schools.com/php/php_oop_static_methods.asp

- abstract - when the parent class has a named method, but need its child class(es) to fill out the tasks - https://www.w3schools.com/php/php_oop_classes_abstract.asp


    public - the property or method can be accessed from everywhere. This is default
    protected - the property or method can be accessed within the class and by classes derived from that class
    private - the property or method can ONLY be accessed within the class
